title: Hour 2 - Chris Mannix, Ed Reed
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Chris Mannix, Ed Reed
description:
Dan talks to NBA Insider Chris Mannix to get the skinny on the situation with Boston Celtics HC Ime Udoka. And he talks with NFL Hall of Famer Ed Reed about last night's game and the rest of the league.
